{"tid":856110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］［突發］有人勒索我朋友","createTime":"2018-10-10T11:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T01:56:27.000Z","uid":204982,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7a520b16468538d67007093994ae44e8c53ef64d","tid":856110,"uid":204982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:48:20.000Z","msg":"事源係咁<br />\n我朋友之前向呢位小姐借咗個風筒<br />\n但個風筒入面已經磨蝕哂，本身已經壞壞地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢位小姐就用個風筒做藉口，叫我朋友賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我朋友願意承擔責任，賠一個全新同型號既風筒俾佢（即使並非佢整爛，但都唔好傷和氣）<br />\n但呢位小姐獅子開大口，屈我朋友賠4000蚊畀佢（市價1xxx)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連月黎不停用佢父母名義勒索我朋友<br />\n仲變本加厲，冒簽老豆簽名<br />\nsend咗張投訴信畀我朋友學校校長、老師，搞我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢位小姐為咗嗰4000蚊，偽造文件，勒索人錢，仲話已經報咗警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （佢依家喺加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n各位連登大大，應該點做好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/194625_57c766765c1793e3318ff1251fcff4e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F194625_57c766765c1793e3318ff1251fcff4e2.png&h=a25da667&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/194642_8ae7b13a744bcc33045b82bac3a63027.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F194642_8ae7b13a744bcc33045b82bac3a63027.png&h=cd24fd83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"058f74051d0071beed0d48c2fabf02ca40674812","tid":856110,"uid":204982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img 